RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT Portfolio,Portfolio_Desc FROM Tltms_Portfolio WHERE Branch = ? AND Desk_Code = ? AND NVL(LMA_PARTICIPATION,'N') ='N'

SELECT a.Product_Code, a.Product_Description FROM Oltms_Product a WHERE Module = 'TL' AND Product_Type = 'T' AND Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A' AND a.Product_Code IN (SELECT c.Product_Code FROM Olvw_Avl_Prod_Br_Usr c, Olvw_User_Products s WHERE s.User_Id = c.User_Id AND s.Product_Code = c.Product_Code AND a.Product_Code = c.Product_Code AND s.User_Id = Global.User_Id) ORDER BY 1
SELECT Expense_Code FROM Tltm_Portfolio_Expcode_Detail WHERE Portfolio = ?

SELECT a.Position_Identifier, a.Portfolio, a.Branch, a.Desk_Code, a.Position_Qualifier, Decode(a.Identifier_Type, 'W', 'Swap', 'T', 'Silent', 'S', 'Self') Identifier_Type, a.Firm_Acct_Mnemonic FROM Tlvws_Position_Detail a WHERE a.Branch = Global.Current_Branch AND NVL(A.LMA_PARTICIPATION,'N') ='N' AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND a.Auth_Stat = 'A' ORDER BY 1
SELECT b.Customer_No, b.Customer_Name1, b.Short_Name FROM Oltms_Customer b WHERE b.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND b.Record_Stat = 'O' ORDER BY 1
SELECT Ccy_Code, Ccy_Name FROM Cytms_Ccy_Defn WHERE Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A' ORDER BY 1
SELECT Broker, NAME FROM Bktms_Brmaster WHERE Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A' ORDER BY Broker

(SELECT a.Firm_Acct_Mnemonic, b.Expense_Code FROM Oltms_Firmac_Mapping a, Oltms_Firmac_Map_Detail b WHERE a.Firm_Acct_Mnemonic = b.Firm_Acct_Mnemonic AND b.Expense_Code = ? AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND a.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND ? IS NULL)UNION (SELECT Firm_Acct_Mnemonic, Firm_Acct_Mnemonic FROM Tltms_Portfolio WHERE Portfolio = ? AND Firm_Acct_Mnemonic IS NOT NULL AND ? IS NOT NULL)

SELECT DISTINCT a.Trade_Ref_No, a.Ext_Contract_Ref_No FROM Tltbs_Upload_Master a WHERE a.Branch = Global.Current_Branch /*AND (a.source_code = 'LQT')*/ AND a.Version_No = (SELECT MAX(Version_No) FROM Tltbs_Upload_Master WHERE Ext_Contract_Ref_No = a.Ext_Contract_Ref_No) AND (a.Process_Status = 'P' OR (a.Process_Status = 'R' AND a.Auth_Status = 'A')) AND a.Module = 'TL' AND a.Source_Code <> 'LSORIG' AND a.Trade_Ref_No IS NOT NULL AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Oltbs_Contract WHERE Contract_Ref_No = a.Trade_Ref_No AND Contract_Status <> 'V')

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: Branch = Global.Current_Branch and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = PRODUCT_CODE AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
